Backslash should not escape the final backtick of verbatim

```
`verbatim\`
.
<p><code>verbatim\</code></p>
```

Should work the same with longer sequences of backticks

```
``verbatim\``
.
<p><code>verbatim\</code></p>
```

Backslash should not escape when using extra space

```
`` `verbatim\` ``
.
<p><code>`verbatim\`</code></p>
```

Backslash should not escape in verbatim inside tables

```
| `\` |
.
<table>
<tr>
<td><code>\</code></td>
</tr>
</table>
```
